## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of perspectives covered. Some sources may present biased views based on their economic or political stance. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of globalization means that findings may quickly become outdated. Further research could explore more recent developments and include a broader range of geopolitical contexts.